            <div class="title">
                National Service (Amendment) Bill
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1948-12-01/debates/d859b532-64b0-49f1-b390-be8124a0d1b7/NationalService(Amendment)Money" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
