            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-dbdc4999-875d-4d07-91a6-9e0be4d5de9e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
