                Mr. Smith
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-af4c8e74-026f-4f4f-b7ed-5ad203273b18" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
