        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-20b91d0f-3a18-4a9c-9e31-12d62f8bab3d">
                Mr. Yates
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-20b91d0f-3a18-4a9c-9e31-12d62f8bab3d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-12-01/debates/30d6003c-69fb-40c3-b896-8e3a67f034bd/NationalService(Amendment)Bill#contribution-20b91d0f-3a18-4a9c-9e31-12d62f8bab3d">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">The hon. and gallant Member must not suggest that I have mocked at people in uniform. [HON. MEMBERS: "Yes, you did."] No, because I have too much respect for all those who believe that it is right to serve.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-20b91d0f-3a18-4a9c-9e31-12d62f8bab3d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
