                Mr. A. R. W. Low  (Blackpool, North)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-c9bf54a4-c16f-4996-89f4-12811959a453" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
