<p class="">I am obliged to the right hon. Gentleman. Not a single word about 1939. And why? Because nobody has more experience, and indeed bitter experience, of the result of lack of preparation before 1939 than the right hon. Gentleman.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
