        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-323f94d2-92a0-4f8a-b48a-9b74bb31b8cc'>
            
<p class="">and amenities in the Army and the contentment that arises from happy relations in the Army that will induce men who are called up under National Service to remain as Regular soldiers. That is all I want to say to the House.</p>
